    "Id": "vehicledef_POLEMOS_LRM",
    "Name": "Polemos (LRM)",
    "Details": "Developed as a replacement for the ageing Indra APC, the Polemos is a 40 ton APC primordially meant for use by Solhama clusters. Armed with an array of lighter weapons the Polemos has a 5 ton cargo bay and is powered by a 220 rated Fuel Cell; allowing it to reach speeds of nearly 100kph. The LRM version is armed with an LRM-15 and 4 Light Machine Guns. Introduced by the Hell's Horses, it has since seen use with every other clan.\n\n<b><color=#ffcc00>Fuel Cell: Improved vehicle engine that works in a Vacuum.</color></b>\n\n<b><color=#ffcc00>Movement: 6/9 Hex: 180/270 Meters.</color></b>\n\n<color=#ffcc00><b>Armor:</b> Ferro-Fibrous (C)\n<b>Structure:</b> Limited Amphibious\n<b>Values       A        S  </b>\n<b>Front</b>       150     20\n<b>Left</b>         125     20\n<b>Right</b>       125     20\n<b>Rear</b>        100     20\n<b>Turret</b>      125     20\n\n<b>Total</b>      625    100</color>\n\n<color=#ff0000>Quirk: Easy to Pilot</color>",
